00:40:33.134 --> 00:40:34.573
Gilligan, why
don't you stop that.

525
00:40:34.653 --> 00:40:37.293
Come on, no Whammies! No Whammies!
No Whammies! Stop!

526
00:40:37.375 --> 00:40:39.533
For weather on
the ones, here's Lester.

