00:40:43.294 --> 00:40:46.094
Hey, man, this
time we'll do it my way.

530
00:40:46.174 --> 00:40:47.214
Ooh!

531
00:40:52.735 --> 00:40:54.573
Well, hello, puppy.

532
00:40:54.654 --> 00:40:57.774
